data.description: Welcome to 234 Golden Gate Drive in the lovely area of Valemont Heights. Move in ready. This 4 bedroom, one and a half bath home has been well maintained and freshly painted from top to bottom!! Inside you'll find beautiful hard wood flooring in the living room that flows into the dining room. Kitchen is done with lovely ceramic tile. Second floor boasts 4 bedrooms and one full bath. Use the 4th bedroom to fit your needs such as an office/den. Enjoy your summers on the back deck with privacy of a fenced in yard while cooling off with your in-ground pool. This home is perfect for a first time home buyer or for the couple starting a young family!!
